    "Around 1880, she became a pupil of August Alleb\u00e9 (1838-1927) at the Amsterdam Academy of Fine Arts.": [],
    "In 1883, she settled in The Hague as a painter.": [],
    "Her works, drawings, watercolors, and paintings, mostly kept in private collections, are not widely known.": [],
    "Letters written by the painter Jan Toorop (1858-1928) to Marius reveal some information on her work.": [
