    "Between 1895 and 1907, she was an art critic for the newspaper <em>Het Vaderland</em>, and subsequently, until 1916, for <em>Het Nieuws van den Dag</em>.": [],
    "In 1917 she coauthored a monograph on Johannes Bosboom (1817-1891) with <a href=\"/martinw\">Wilhelm Martin</a>.": [
